 John E. Hall, music director of the Cypress Pops Orchestra, is forming a new 
orchestra to be called the Philharmonic Orchestra of Cypress. The all-volunteer 
group will begin rehearsing March 2. Musicians interested in participating 
should call Hall evenings at (714) 527-0964. 
