<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHARGES IN ICE CREAM KILLING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Three 16-year-old boys have been charged with murder in the shooting death of 
an ice cream truck driver, police said Tuesday. 
</P>
