He can't help it that he's been out of school for five weeks because the quake 
did so much damage (above). On his first day back Tuesday, looking for his 
temporary classroom, Jeff showed he's been away too long. "(Someone) told me 
that way was south, so I figured that the other way was north.". . . He wasn't 
the only one confused. (B1) 
