 The incident: Shot in the wake of a rampage at a state unemployment office 
Dec. 2 in which three others were killed. 
</P>
<P>
 Status of investigation: The gunman, Alan Winterbourne, was shot to death 
minutes later by police outside another unemployment office in Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Family: Married, with two children. 
</P>
<P>
 Quote: "If they need cops in heaven, they got a good one in Jim O'Brien." Rev. 
