<DOCNO> LA022394-0184 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 016410 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
