<P>
 NATO and Bosnia -- A map that was part of a graphic published Sunday dealing 
with the possibility of NATO air raids in Bosnia-Herzegovina erred in locating 
an air base in Villafranca, Spain. The base in question is in Villafranca, near 
Verona, in northern Italy. 
